                            <comment id="15404373" author="jahewson" created="Tue, 2 Aug 2016 16:54:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;SCALE_TO_FIT is the default behaviour, so it doesn&apos;t need checking for. But STRETCH_TO_FIT needs to be checked in the same manner as SHRINK_TO_FIT currently is - so that looks like a bug.&lt;/p&gt;

